        <li><strong>Social media cookies</strong> – to enable sharing content across platforms.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>How Can You Control Cookies?</h3>
      <p>
        You have the right to decide whether to accept or reject cookies.
        You can manage your preferences via your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies
        may impact your ability to use certain features of our website.
      </p>

